To add these two numbers together, we align them appropriately and perform column-wise addition:

\[
\begin{array}{r}
   & 2 & 2 & 1 & 1 & 0 & 0 & 0 & 0_3 \\
 + & 1 & 1 & 0 & 1 & 2 & 0 & 0 & 1_3 \\
\hline
   & 3 & 0 & 2 & 0 & 1 & 0 & 0 & 1_3 \\
\end{array}
\]

Therefore, \( 221100002_{3} + 110120012_{3} = 30201001_{3} \).